author: Daniel Peters
title: Tinder profile of Queensland rapist Douglas Steele found | Daily Mail Online
text: 'I'm a feminist and consider myself on the left of politics': The chilling Tinder profile of university staffer rapist who molested a student, 20, as she slept James Cook University employee Douglas Steele convicted of raping a student The father-of-three's Tinder bio said he was a 'feminist' on the 'left of politics' He pleaded guilty last month to digitally raping the student in September 2015 He was watching football with a student and her then-boyfriend at the time Student passed out in room and he entered under pretense of checking on her WARNING: Graphic content is contained in this story Published: 05:00 GMT, 1 February 2017 | Updated: 08:58 GMT, 1 February 2017 712 shares
